{"body": "It might be helpful to describe the effects of binding events to a selector that gets replaced. It is an easy thing to overlook as a JS noob. The 'on' function provides a facility for handling this problem by binding higher in the DOM hierarchy, and it also might be nice to expose the different ways to use on. This is all in the jQuery documentation so this may be a moot point. ", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9213255", "created_at": "2012-10-07T22:27:49Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7493#issuecomment-9213255", "updated_at": "2012-10-07T22:27:49Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7493, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jeremywrowe", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/5b9aedbcfca85ad2f60bd4a25e445b4d?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fb61a3fe302255c95a3282ff2c2bbb141.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/received_events", "gravatar_id": "5b9aedbcfca85ad2f60bd4a25e445b4d", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jeremywrowe", "type": "User", "id": 396364, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jeremywrowe/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523de79dbd354364b900b3b9"}, "id": 9213255, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7493"}
